{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言，見染絲者而嘆曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言，見染絲者而嘆曰：", "canonical_ref": "3.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "染於蒼則蒼，染於黃則黃，所入者變，其色亦變。", "text_normalized": "染於蒼則蒼，染於黃則黃，所入者變，其色亦變。", "canonical_ref": "3.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "五入必而已，則為五色矣。", "text_normalized": "五入必而已，則為五色矣。", "canonical_ref": "3.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "故染不可不愼也。", "text_normalized": "故染不可不愼也。", "canonical_ref": "3.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "非獨染絲然也，國亦有染。", "text_normalized": "非獨染絲然也，國亦有染。", "canonical_ref": "3.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "舜染於許由、伯陽，禹染於皋陶、伯益，湯染於伊尹、仲虺，武王染於太公、周公。", "text_normalized": "舜染於許由、伯陽，禹染於皋陶、伯益，湯染於伊尹、仲虺，武王染於太公、周公。", "canonical_ref": "3.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "此四王者所染當，故王天下，立為天子，功名蔽天地。", "text_normalized": "此四王者所染當，故王天下，立為天子，功名蔽天地。", "canonical_ref": "3.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "舉天下之仁義顯人，必稱此四王者。", "text_normalized": "舉天下之仁義顯人，必稱此四王者。", "canonical_ref": "3.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "夏桀染於干辛、推哆，殷紂染於崇侯、惡來，厲王染於厲公長父、榮夷終，幽王染於傅公夷、蔡公穀。", "text_normalized": "夏桀染於干辛、推哆，殷紂染於崇侯、惡來，厲王染於厲公長父、榮夷終，幽王染於傅公夷、蔡公穀。", "canonical_ref": "3.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "此四王者所染不當，故國殘身死，為天下僇。", "text_normalized": "此四王者所染不當，故國殘身死，為天下僇。", "canonical_ref": "3.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "舉天下不義辱人，必稱此四王者。", "text_normalized": "舉天下不義辱人，必稱此四王者。", "canonical_ref": "3.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "齊桓染於管仲、鮑叔，晉文染於舅犯、高偃，楚莊染於孫叔、沈尹，吳闔閭染於伍員、文義，越句踐染於范蠡大夫種。", "text_normalized": "齊桓染於管仲、鮑叔，晉文染於舅犯、高偃，楚莊染於孫叔、沈尹，吳闔閭染於伍員、文義，越句踐染於范蠡大夫種。", "canonical_ref": "3.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "此五君者所染當，故霸諸侯，功名傳於後世。", "text_normalized": "此五君者所染當，故霸諸侯，功名傳於後世。", "canonical_ref": "3.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "范吉射染於長柳朔、王胜，中行寅染於籍秦、高彊，吳夫差染於王孫雒、太宰嚭，智伯搖染於智國、張武，中山尚染於魏義、偃長，宋康染於唐鞅、佃不禮。", "text_normalized": "范吉射染於長柳朔、王胜，中行寅染於籍秦、高彊，吳夫差染於王孫雒、太宰嚭，智伯搖染於智國、張武，中山尚染於魏義、偃長，宋康染於唐鞅、佃不禮。", "canonical_ref": "3.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "此六君者所染不當，故國家殘亡，身為刑戮，宗廟破滅，絕無後類，君臣離散，民人流亡。", "text_normalized": "此六君者所染不當，故國家殘亡，身為刑戮，宗廟破滅，絕無後類，君臣離散，民人流亡。", "canonical_ref": "3.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "舉天下之貪暴苛擾者，必稱此六君也。", "text_normalized": "舉天下之貪暴苛擾者，必稱此六君也。", "canonical_ref": "3.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "凡君之所以安者，何也？", "text_normalized": "凡君之所以安者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "3.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "以其行理也，行理性於染當。", "text_normalized": "以其行理也，行理性於染當。", "canonical_ref": "3.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "故善為君者，勞於論人，而佚於治官。", "text_normalized": "故善為君者，勞於論人，而佚於治官。", "canonical_ref": "3.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "不能為君者，傷形費神，愁心勞意，然國逾危，身逾辱。", "text_normalized": "不能為君者，傷形費神，愁心勞意，然國逾危，身逾辱。", "canonical_ref": "3.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "此六君者，非不重其國，愛其身也，以不知要故也。", "text_normalized": "此六君者，非不重其國，愛其身也，以不知要故也。", "canonical_ref": "3.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "不知要者，所染不當也。", "text_normalized": "不知要者，所染不當也。", "canonical_ref": "3.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "非獨國有染也，士亦有染。", "text_normalized": "非獨國有染也，士亦有染。", "canonical_ref": "3.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "其友皆好仁義，淳謹畏令，則家日益，身日安，名日榮，處官得其理矣，則段干木、禽子、傅說之徒是也。", "text_normalized": "其友皆好仁義，淳謹畏令，則家日益，身日安，名日榮，處官得其理矣，則段干木、禽子、傅說之徒是也。", "canonical_ref": "3.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "其友皆好矜奮，創作比周，則家日損、身日危、名日辱，處官失其理矣，則子西、易牙、豎刀之徒是也。", "text_normalized": "其友皆好矜奮，創作比周，則家日損、身日危、名日辱，處官失其理矣，則子西、易牙、豎刀之徒是也。", "canonical_ref": "3.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "《詩》曰「必擇所堪。", "text_normalized": "《詩》曰「必擇所堪。", "canonical_ref": "3.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable", "source_id": "mozi-003-that-which-is-affectable__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "」必謹所堪者，此之謂也。", "text_normalized": "」必謹所堪者，此之謂也。", "canonical_ref": "3.27", "notes": ""}
